# Project & Tooling

Single-repo **Tauri 2** desktop app. TypeScript frontend + Rust backend in one workspace.

Related docs: [DESIGN_DOC.mdc](DESIGN_DOC.mdc), [TAURI.mdc](TAURI.mdc), [FRONTEND.mdc](FRONTEND.mdc), [UI.mdc](UI.mdc).

Root guides: [README.md](../README.md), [RUNNING.md](../RUNNING.md), [CONTRIBUTING.md](../CONTRIBUTING.md).

---

## Repository layout

```
orbit/
  src/                     # React frontend (Vite)
    app/                   # App shell, providers
    features/              # Screen-level pages
    components/            # Shared UI
    controllers/           # Gamepad + spatial focus
    hooks/                 # React hooks
    stores/                # Zustand state
    themes/                # Built-in theme definitions + layout hooks
    lib/                   # Tauri wrappers, formatters, artwork helpers
    types/                 # Shared TS types
    styles/                # Global CSS + theme tokens
  src-tauri/               # Rust backend
    src/
      commands/            # Tauri invoke handlers
      database/            # SQLite migrations + repository
      importers/           # Platform importers
      launching/           # Launch + process monitor + sessions
      models/              # Shared Rust structs
      services/            # Library sync, artwork
      utils/               # Paths, filenames, size
    icons/                 # App icons
    Cargo.toml
  e2e/                     # Playwright specs
  docs/                    # Design & architecture docs
  .cursor/rules/           # Cursor agent rules
  package.json
  vite.config.ts
  tailwind.config.js
  playwright.config.ts
```

---

## Prerequisites

- macOS 12+
- Node.js 22+
- Yarn 1.x or compatible
- Rust stable (`rustup`)
- Xcode Command Line Tools

---

## Scripts

| Script | Command | Description |
| ------ | ------- | ----------- |
| `dev` | `vite` | Frontend only (mock Tauri API) |
| `tauri:dev` | `tauri dev` | Full desktop app in development |
| `tauri:build` | `tauri build` | Release `.app` bundle |
| `release:macos` | `bash scripts/release-macos.sh` | Build + package macOS artifacts to `release/<version>/` |
| `build` | `tsc --noEmit && vite build` | Typecheck + frontend production build |
| `typecheck` | `tsc --noEmit` | TypeScript only |
| `format` | `prettier --write .` | Format all files |
| `format:check` | `prettier --check .` | CI-style format gate |
| `test:rust` | `cargo test --manifest-path src-tauri/Cargo.toml` | Rust unit tests |
| `test:e2e` | `playwright test` | Browser E2E (mock API or Tauri webview) |
| `test:e2e:ui` | `playwright test --ui` | Playwright UI mode |

Typical dev loop:

```bash
yarn install
yarn tauri:dev
```

