## CI (planned)

GitHub Actions workflows:

| Workflow | Trigger | Purpose |
| -------- | ------- | ------- |
| [deploy-pages.yml](../.github/workflows/deploy-pages.yml) | Push to `main` (`docs/**`) or manual | Publish landing page to GitHub Pages |
| [release.yml](../.github/workflows/release.yml) | Push tag `v*` | Build macOS `.dmg` and publish GitHub Release |

Future CI should mirror local gates:

1. `yarn run format:check`
2. `yarn run typecheck`
3. `yarn run test:rust`
4. `yarn run build`
5. `yarn run test:e2e` (optional job with Playwright)

